4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior experience, aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program covers essential skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, focusing on cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. It includes 16 weeks of training with three live online classes per week, limited to 16 students per class. Participants receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop